# 🛍️ Discvrai - Product Discovery with AI Assist

![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-1.0.0-blue)
![React](https://img.shields.io/badge/React-18.2.0-61dafb)
![Node](https://img.shields.io/badge/Node.js-18.x-339933)
![Express](https://img.shields.io/badge/Express-4.18.2-000000)
![Gemini AI](https://img.shields.io/badge/Gemini_AI-Free-8E75B2)

A full-stack product discovery application that leverages **Google's Gemini AI** to provide natural language product search and recommendations. Users can browse products or ask questions in plain English to find exactly what they're looking for.

---

##  Features

-  **Natural Language Search** - Ask questions like "Show me laptops under $2000" or "What's good for gaming?"
-  **Product Catalog** - Browse 45+ products across multiple categories
-  **AI-Powered Responses** - Gemini AI interprets queries and recommends relevant products
-  **Real-time Results** - Instant AI responses with product matches
-  **Responsive Design** - Beautiful UI that works on all devices
-  **Example Queries** - One-click example questions to get started

---

##  Tech Stack

### Backend
- **Node.js** - Runtime environment
- **Express** - Web framework
- **Google Generative AI** - Gemini AI SDK
- **CORS** - Cross-origin resource sharing
- **Dotenv** - Environment variables

### Frontend
- **React** - UI library
- **Axios** - HTTP client
- **CSS3** - Styling with modern features

---

##  Live Demo

